OL,3,CMurder probe launched after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing near school in Hackney
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a man in his 20s was
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed near an east London
OL,9,Fschool.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to reports of a
OL,12,Fstabbing at Downs Park Road in Hackney
OL,13,Fat 1.42pm on Monday.
OL,15,FThe man died at the scene and no
OL,16,Farrests have been made, the
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police said.
OL,19,FThe force does not believe any pupils
OL,20,Fat the school were involved and it is
OL,21,Fbeing treating as an isolated incident.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/4
