OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784126889
OL,3,CMurder probe launched after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing near school in Hackney
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Wayne
OL,7,FJolley, from the Met's Specialist
OL,8,FCrime Command, said: "Our
OL,9,Finvestigation remains in the early
OL,10,Fstages and officers are working at
OL,11,Fpace to identify those responsible.
OL,13,F"Police will remain in the area
OL,14,Fovernight as our inquiries continue,
OL,15,Fand I encourage anyone with any
OL,16,Finformation to contact us."
OL,26,@pD@VOUuD@AOUxD@[O]
