OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1784126889
OL,3,CMurder probe launched after fatal
OL,4,Cstabbing near school in Hackney
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent
OL,7,FBrittany Clarke said: "We understand
OL,8,Fthat this incident occurred close to a
OL,9,Fschool in broad daylight, which will
OL,10,Fbe hugely concerning for local
OL,11,Fresidents.
OL,13,F"We don't believe this to involve any
OL,14,Fpupils at the school and are treating
OL,15,Fthis as an isolated incident."
OL,17,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,18,Fcontact police on 101 quoting
OL,19,Freference 4139/13JUL, or anonymously
OL,20,Fthrough Crimestoppers.
OL,26,@oD@WOUuD@AOUwD@^O]
